{
    "title": "Batuque na Cozinha",
    "artist": "Pixinguinha",
    "composer": "",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Batuque na cozinha</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sinhá não quer</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Por causa do batuque</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu queimei meu pé</span>\n\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não moro em casa de cômodo</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não é por ter medo não</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Na cozinha muita gente sempre dá em alteração</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Batuque na cozinha</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sinhá não quer</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Por causa do batuque</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu queimei meu pé</span>\n\n                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#°\">D#°</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Então não bula na cumbuca</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não me espante o rato</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Se o branco tem ciúme</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que dirá o mulato</span>\n\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#°\">D#°</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu fui na cozinha</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pra ver uma cebola</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E o branco com ciúme</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">De uma tal crioula</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#°\">D#°</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Deixei a cebola, peguei a batata</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E o branco com ciúme de uma tal mulata</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#°\">D#°</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Peguei o balaio pra medir a farinha</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E o branco com ciúme de uma tal branquinha</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Então não bula na cumbuca</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não me espante o rato</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Se o branco tem ciúme</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que dirá o mulato</span>\n\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas o batuque na cozinha</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sinhá não quer</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Por causa do batuque</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu queimei meu pé</span>\n\n                                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu fui na cozinha pra tomar um café</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E o malandro ta de olho na minha mulher</span>\n                                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas, comigo eu apelei pra desarmonia</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E fomos lá direto pra delegacia</span>\n                                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Seu comissário foi dizendo com altivez</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E da casa de cômodo da tal Inês</span>\n                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Revistem os dois, botem no xadrez</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Malandro comigo não tem vez</span>\n\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Batuque na cozinha</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sinhá não quer</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Por causa do batuque</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu queimei meu pé</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas seu comissário</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu estou com a razão</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu não moro na casa de arrumação</span>\n                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu fui apanhar o meu violão</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que estava empenhado com salomão</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu pago a fiança com satisfação</span>\n                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas não me bota no xadrez</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com esse malandrão</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que faltou com respeito a um cidadão</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que é paraíba do norte, maranhão</span>\n",
